","msg":"內蒙就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會去下蒙古, 真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:07:00.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"05df047b31e78d3ebfd988318e55781ffb66fe07","tid":591464,"uid":86684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"內蒙古9成漢人，但個景ok既，可以去下沙漠同草原。<br />\n呼和浩特市中心就真係似大陸二，三線城市"},{"pid":"f0273372dbe29922ebf2c38969d827c1c08ac812","tid":591464,"uid":83217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"雲南"},{"pid":"373f98c792ec604cf0d316fc3114ae5f507d6eff","tid":591464,"uid":36750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"北疆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde5da00a62e32dd9f03a1042d2f710c24f63875","tid":591464,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f267c5f498ddd55de959a0f0597d883f84d47a9d","tid":591464,"uid":22876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"去過青海內蒙外蒙<br />\n青海每個景點之間好遠 <br />\n同車女朋友嘔左幾次<br />\n但景點就比較大型又有特色<br />\n例如門源花海同天空之鏡 <br />\n<br />\n內蒙就真係無咩特色<br />\n係得草原同商業味濃既蒙古包區<br />\n外蒙起碼有真蒙古人同有座成吉思汗像<br />\n<br />\n未去過西藏<br />\n但我相信以上黎講<br />\n新疆自然景觀應該最屈機<br />\n香港人去又文化衝擊大"},{"pid":"5cd77976691958c480fe7af2dc7a7b90cf6951a6","tid":591464,"uid":142964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc3c1515a7a3a317fe33b4b1261df44c11c0ce06","tid":591464,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"無錢去歐洲<br />\n睇景黎講去西藏青海新疆内蒙古邊個地方最正<br />\n大約去十日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"新疆10日唔夠，秋天最好<br />\n<br />\n西藏10日勉強玩到兩湖一峰+市內，除冬天外都好ok<br />\n<br />\n青海+西寧唔洗10日，玩10日好輕鬆行程，夏秋較靚<br />\n<br />\n內蒙睇你去邊，10日玩到一部份，4季都有野睇<br />\n<br />\n全部去過，睇季節，各有各好。"},{"pid":"537f65fddac6dc4dd18b80dfb6ae86a14643c83c","tid":591464,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"青海敦煌線<br />\n<br />\n但啲嘢食真心差 有生以黎食得最差個一星期<br />\n第二就係旱廁問題 好撚嘔心"},{"pid":"96e7496a4952e7c9ed57bf24b09d54d2140688ca","tid":591464,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537f65fddac6dc4dd18b80dfb6ae86a14643c83c","tid":591464,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"青海敦煌線<br />\n<br />\n但啲嘢食真心差 有生以黎食得最差個一星期<br />\n第二就係旱廁問題 好撚嘔心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"食痾訓都差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52a446b2676d2d8f16e9d11d31ba4113ca9f97c","tid":591464,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"新疆"},{"pid":"a816fe9385e39b273543028047e3747e36795958","tid":591464,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96e7496a4952e7c9ed57bf24b09d54d2140688ca","tid":591464,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537f65fddac6dc4dd18b80dfb6ae86a14643c83c","tid":591464,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"青海敦煌線<br />\n<br />\n但啲嘢食真心差 有生以黎食得最差個一星期<br />\n第二就係旱廁問題 好撚嘔心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"食痾訓都差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"訓反而ok 正常酒店房"},{"pid":"98b069c0822f93004c29f8c6566531ae22ca796e","tid":591464,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd77976691958c480fe7af2dc7a7b90cf6951a6","tid":591464,"uid":142964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc3c1515a7a3a317fe33b4b1261df44c11c0ce06","tid":591464,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"無錢去歐洲<br />\n睇景黎講去西藏青海新疆内蒙古邊個地方最正<br 